  "text": "As discussed in the literature, the financial development variable is highly likely to be endogenous, possibly due to feedback from income inequality to financial development. To deal with the endogeneity issue and account for the threshold nonlinearity simultaneously, the instrumental variable (IV) threshold regression technique suggested by [CITATION_1] is employed, where Equation (1) can take the following form:",
